      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CINEMATIC (1) missed the frame last time at Ballarat but the start prior rocketed around 390m at Ballarat in 22.14. Rates a top chance if runs up to time two back. BORROLOOLA BOY (8) had been in great form but was out of the placings last run, finishing fourth (19.39) in a Mix 6/7 FIN at this track. Shuffled back off the inside last time. Can do much better this time. KUEBIKO (2) finished campaign in the minors over 305m at Mt Gambier, overcoming a check in a Grade 6 to finish third (17.86). Expecting another bold showing. BE LIVELY (3) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
